      "description": "Hey there! You honestly won't find another one like this. It's been my absolute pride and joy, kept in a climate-controlled garage and hand-washed every single week. It looks and drives just like it did the day it rolled off the lot\u2014totally flawless inside and out. If you're looking for perfection, this is the one! Come take a look, you won't be disappointed! \u2728",
