    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting a collector-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in pristine condition. This example features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering 333 hp through six individual throttle bodies and a precision-tuned high-pressure VANOS variable valve timing system. The chassis remains exceptionally rigid, featuring a fully documented subframe reinforcement and a refreshed suspension geometry. Power is managed via a Getrag 6-speed close-ratio manual transmission and a factory variable M-differential lock. Finished in Carbon Black Metallic, the exterior retains its factory depth, while the Nappa leather interior shows no signs of bolster wear or UV degradation. Mechanically flawless, the naturally aspirated powerplant pulls linearly to its 8,000 RPM redline. An investment-grade specimen for the discerning purist.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
