    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy it! This car is in absolutely pristine, mint condition\u2014it\u2019s basically been pampered since day one. No dings, no scratches, and it still has that fresh car feel. It drives like an absolute dream! If you're looking for something that feels brand new without the showroom price tag, this is the one for you. I'd love for you to come see it in person and fall in love with it just like I did!",
      "price": 46500.0,
