    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade E46 M3 in concours-level condition. This example features the legendary S54 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies and a precision-tuned double VANOS system. The Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission provides tactile engagement, paired with a factory-calibrated M-Variable differential lock for optimal torque distribution. Mechanical integrity is paramount: the rear subframe has been proactively reinforced, and the rod bearings have been replaced to ensure peak operational longevity. The chassis remains exceptionally rigid, supported by a refreshed suspension geometry and factory-spec bushings that preserve the car\u2019s renowned 50/50 weight distribution. Finished in Carbon Black over Nappa leather, the aesthetic remains as sharp as the day it left Regensburg. A turn-key masterpiece for the discerning collector.",
